hints.content: When we skip count by fives,  we add $5$ to each number as we count.

Fati started with $810$,  so we need to add $5$ more to $810$.

$810 + 5 = 815$

The next number Fati will say is $815$.

Fati is still skip counting by fives so we need to add $5$ to $815$.

$815 + 5 = 820$

The next number Fati will say is $820$.
